*envchain-1.0.0 (12 Jun 2016)

  12 Jun 2016; Patrice Clement <monsieurp@gentoo.org> +envchain-1.0.0.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  Add new ebuild to the tree.

  envchain allows to save credentials or any secret values in a secure vault,
  via
  libsecret/gnome-keyring for Linux, in order to avoid writing credentials to
  a
  flat file.

  Gentoo-Bug: https://bugs.gentoo.org/585634
  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28
